<br>
The rune also keeps you alive through an extra AE or two.  Yes, a well-played wizard will keep deliberate aggro off of himself, but you cannot stop AEs.<br>
<br>
The mana regen you cannot argue with.  3pt is 2 points more than manaskin, and 1 point more than Breeze.  So this is mini-clarity for you that stacks WITH c2, potg, gob/m/i, all that fun stuff.<br>
<br>
Free.<br>
<br>
